jobs.description: We are looking for a Product Designer to work on various products we develop for our customers. Product Designer responsibilities include defining product specifications, creating digital or print drawings, and designing fully-functional products. To be successful in this role, you should have an eye for color and shape and be able to translate requirements into practical product features.
jobs.responsibilities:
Roles & Responsibilities:

  • Work closely with product managers, engineers, and other designers to ensure designs are implemented correctly.
  • Continuously improve design processes and methodologies.
  • Analyze how a new product ties in with market needs and consumer preferences
  • Research materials and techniques
  • Use 3D modeling software to design products and components
  • Designing and creating products based on specifications and best practices
  • Creating presentations to showcase ideas or provide updates on project progress
  • Completing competitor analyses to ensure the originality of their designs
  • Researching consumer trends and gathering data to support design choices
  • Using a variety of manual, automated, and digital design tools to complete work

Requirements:

  • At least 2 years of experience in product design.
  • Strong portfolio showcasing design process and outcomes.
  • Proficient in design tools such as Sketch, Figma, or Adobe Creative Suite.
  • Strong knowledge of design principles, typography, and color theory.
  • Experience conducting user research and usability testing.
  • Excellent communication skills and ability to collaborate with cross-functional teams.
jobs.skills: coral draw and photo shop, Figma
jobs.title: Graphics Designer

jobs.description: We are looking to hire a dedicated content writer to create content for blogs, articles, email copywriting, social media, and the company website. Ultimately, a top-performing Content Writer should be able to contribute to the development of strategies that will increase reader engagement.
jobs.responsibilities:
Content Writer Responsibilities:

  • Conducting in-depth research on industry-related topics in order to develop original content.
  • Developing content for blogs, articles, product descriptions, social media, and the company website.
  • Creating compelling headlines and body copy that will capture the attention of the target audience.
  • Identifying customers needs and recommending new content to address gaps in the company's current content.
  • Editing and polishing existing content to improve readability.
  • Conducting keyword research and using SEO best practices to increase traffic to the company website.

Content Writer Requirements:

  • Proven content writing or copywriting experience.
  • Working knowledge of content management systems.
  • A portfolio of published articles.
  • Excellent writing and editing skills.
  • Effective communication skills.
jobs.skills: Web content writing, SEO Writing, Social media writing
jobs.title: Content Writer
